::KitKat::

She heard Destructor on her link. She sighed and stood up.  She 
smiled and looked at Aracnia. "I have a great many things to attend 
to.  AS the second High Predacon Council member, I shall bid you Good 
day and shall give you a final answer in two days. Thank you for 
joining me today."  She openend her link,"Drillbit, would you be so 
kind as to escort our guests out of the base. Thank you."

She openend her link as she walked out of the conference room,"On my 
way Destructor."


::DarkMouse::
She trembled slightly as she looked at Destructor.
